\details{
The N-BMP dynamics are:
\enumerate{
\item N particles start at positions given by \code{init}.
\item Each particle independently follows the stochastic process.
\item Events occur as a Poisson process with rate \code{N * branching_rate}.
\item At each event, the particle with the largest \code{cost(x)} is removed and
replaced by a copy of a uniformly chosen other particle.
